&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Collection and reporting&amp;nbsp;tools&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    IBM&amp;reg; Rational&amp;reg; Project Conductor&amp;reg; collects Defect by Severity data at the project and program level.&amp;nbsp;IBM&amp;reg;&#xD;
    Rational&amp;reg; ClearQuest Enterprise&amp;reg;,&amp;nbsp;IBM&amp;reg; Rational&amp;reg; Team Concert&amp;reg;, and&amp;nbsp;IBM&amp;reg; Rational&amp;reg; Quality Manager&amp;reg; also&#xD;
    collect Defect Distribution data.&amp;nbsp;IBM&amp;reg; Rational&amp;reg; Insight&amp;reg; reports this metric.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Pitfalls, advice, and countermeasures&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Use the Test Trend (Functional and System) metric as a countermeasure for Defect Distribution to ensure that&#xD;
        sufficient testing has been performed.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></mainDescription>
